Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:07.50,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}想试着谈场猜谜般的恋爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:10.04,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:12.96,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}虽然害怕…但还是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:18.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安稳度日 也太无趣了点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:23.18,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改变些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:26.89,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要个契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:28.56,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飞奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:32.73,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回忆在骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:38.32,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像认识你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:42.45,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不论是晴天雨天还是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:45.20,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:46.62,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从过去到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.87,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从明天到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:50.75,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 时间 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:56.55,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前烦恼的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:02.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}来展开新的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:07.52,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}又在做梦吗？现在的梦还不能说！
