Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:13.02,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}下雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:18.11,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不管是怎样的天气 I need you!!
